Reasoning: The paper discusses two multicarrier techniques, GFDN and VOFDM, which are commonly used in communication systems. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.COMM (Communications and Networking). The paper also involves system design and implementation, which falls under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Finally, the paper mentions the use of these techniques in multimedia applications, which could be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia).
